Dialogs.Dialog: Manaka
Hey, hey. ▲主人公＊▲.
What's wrong ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Can we solve this problem together？
Let's see...
...Hehe.
Hmm？
Your confidence is inspiring. You're doing your best.
I can't lose to you.
I was going to do my best together so, from now on... let me be next to you. I'm kidding.
(Yay！)
Manaka
Hey, the results of the math quiz――
Hehe. It's looking good, isn't it？
Yay！ I'm kidding.
I'm glad you thought you'd get good results.
Why did you think that？
You answered my questions fluently, and you were working truly hard...
...My favorite person is truly...
Ah, no, what I was... That, you know... Let's continue doing our best next time, okay？
(Okay, I'll do my best！)
(I did my best this time！)
Manaka
How can the sensei come up with a surprising solution like that？
Oh, that. I came up with it during preparation.
That shows the results of your everyday efforts. It's amazing, I want to be your apprentice.
You are already one！ I was just imitating you ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Hehe！ It's a little strange. Two people learning from each other.
That reminds me...
From now on, let's do our best while learning from each other, okay？
(Alright, I can't wait！)
Should I solve it like this？ I understand it now. Okay, next problem...
Manaka
...Hehe！
Huh？ What's wrong？
You've been studying with a smile on your face recently.
You're doing excellent, maybe because we're together like this.
When you say that, it makes me want to do my best too, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Me too. I'll do my best, if you tell me to.
Perhaps that is what make us give our best.
Of course！ That's why... We will always be together, right？
(Alright！！ I got my energy back！)
Manaka
You're the only one who could solve that problem.
Do you mean you couldn't solve it, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Nope. Do you want to brag about it？ I'm kidding.
Haha！ If I brag about it, it's going to be more difficult, so I'll refrain from doing it...
Hehe！
But now, you can really solve any problem.
Should I brag about that instead？ ...I'm kidding.
(Let's do our best next time！)
Manaka
▲主人公＊▲.
Umm, why are you angry, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
You're so unfair.
What do you mean？
You did your best studying alone.
Well, it's because I want to be a man who deserves to be with you, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
...Geez.
Well done. I'll be with you next time, okay？
(Yay！)
(I did my best in Modern studies this time！)
Manaka
Was everyone looking at you？ Everyone said your interpretation was so sharp.
You're complimenting me too much.
Isn't it right？ I'm telling the truth.
If you say so, it was worth the effort.
Really？ Then, I'll do it more！ Are you sure it's okay？
I'd feel embarrassed if you do it too much！
Hehe！ Geez, don't say it like that.
You do your best because you're so nice. I'm kidding▼
(I'll continue doing my best！)
Manaka
...*Sigh*.
What's wrong？ You're sighing too much.
I couldn't concentrate on today's class. It's your fault, understand？
My fault！？
Did you guess why by saying it aloud？
You were saying it with a high tone, and your voice was wonderful... I was watching you all the time.
Eh！？ You didn't have to, I didn't do anything that nice.
It was amazing！！ It really was like that to me.
(Yay！)
Manaka
Your essay has become very popular.
I'm really glad I put that much effort.
Hehe. I became one of your fans too▼
For the essay？
For the essay... That too！ I'm kidding.
I will continue to support you with all my strength. Hehe！
(Okay, I'll do my best next time！)
Manaka
You're free now, right？ I really need your help, ▲主人公＊▲.
With what？
Reading comprehension, interpretation, memory and then...
What, that much？
Is that a no？
No, I didn't mean it like that！
Hehe！ I'm sorry.
I don't want the results of your hard work, I want to emulate your hard work.
You look so cool when you are concentrated... Keep up the good work, okay？
(Okay, let's do it！)
Manaka
I want to learn your sense.
I still have along way to go, but thank you.
Even though you do such wonderful works, you still have things to learn？
Okay, aim higher！
Hehe！
I really like that kind of thing...
Hmm？ I couldn't hear that, can you say it once more！
You don't have to polish that sense.... Geez.
(I'm glad I put effort in this！)
Manaka
Wow... Did you make it？
Yeah. Why？
I thought it was wonderful. I wanted to use it to decorate my room.
Really？
Yeah. Hey, everyone can see it.
Yeah, they can see it...
...Would you like to hide it？ With you, for example.
With me？
To keep your work all for yourself. I'm kidding.
(Okay, I'll do my best next time！)
(I really did my best this time！)
Manaka
Your recent work is wonderful. Just by looking at it, warms my heart...
If you say that, then it was worth the effort, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Hehe. You won't get anything if you lie.
Huh？
Geez.
But, I think it's really nice...
I want you to show me more, I'll always be next to you.
(Okay, I'll do my best！)
(I did my best this time！)
Manaka
I like the recent paintings you made.
Really？
Hehe, I'm serious. You deserve all the praise.
It reflects kindness, and the use of colors is amazing...
You make me happy saying those things to me.
...Really？
Yeah, really. So, can you praise me more？
Hehe, geez. Well done▼
(I'll do my best next time！)
Manaka
▲主人公＊▲. Did you take that photo？ It's amazing.
Oh, thank you.
Hey... What do you need to create such a wonderful thing？
Relentless effort... Maybe.
How can I make that effort？ With sense？
How！？ ...Do you want to know the reason why？
You may have been born with it, but there are ways to improve it...
...That's a trade secret！
...Meanie.
It's all fine, because if this happens, you'll be the only one who can see it.
(I have to do my best next time！)
(I did my best this time！)
Manaka
Did you know you have become popular now, because you have a wonderful singing voice？
Haha. Really？
Of course. Everyone was fascinated.
...Everyone... Even you... ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Ah！
...Did you just say "even you"？
The truth is, I want to have you only for myself...
But I want to brag about it a little... Keep doing your best, okay？
(Okay, I'll do my best！)
(I did my best this time！)
Manaka
I've been feeling strange after you perform.
Strange？
Yeah. The sound is so clear... It make me want to listen to it many times.
Whenever you want！
A concert just for me？
Yes. In the music room！
Hehe！ If that happens, should I play the piano too？
(I'll do my best next time！)
(I sang perfectly this time！)
Manaka
▲主人公＊▲！
Ah, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
You were singing with so much passion, even sensei smiled！
I thought that music really makes you enjoy the sound.
Did I look like that？
Hehe, yeah... But...
...But？
I wonder... If I sing with you, I'll also feel good？
(I have to do my best！)
(I think this time it went perfect！)
Manaka
It was amazing. It seems that my knowledge of music is expanding.
Really？ I don't know about that.
It's a lot of fun because I can listen to Chopin and other composers.
I'll be left behind if I don't do my best.
Now, don't exaggerate.
...Hehe！ But, you don't want to be left behind, right？
Even so, I'm a senior in music.
Alright, I'll do my best！
Yes. Hehe！
(It went perfect, I did my best！)
Manaka
During music class, it looks like you're having so much fun and I get lured in too.
I think we can have a lot of fun if you're lured in, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
That'll be ideal, and good results would follow.
I don't think we could have any trouble if you're with me, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
...I'm happy.
I also want to do my best because I have you...
Hehe. Let's continue like this. Let's do our best, okay？
(I'll do my best！)
Manaka
I'm often told that you make a handsome face when singing.
And you think that too, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Yup.
Isn't it wonderful？ I'm so proud of you！
...That's what I want to say. You look so happy.
It's a little embarrassing, but that's what I really feel.
It's your fault. I'm kidding.
(It makes me feel embarrassed... but I'm glad I did my best！)
(I did my best this time！)
Manaka
You're doing amazing these days. You have good times for both short and long distances.
Thank you, I feel great and I'm having fun！
Hmm. Your running pose was so cool. It was really nice――
Hmm？
It's really wonderful... Emm...
What's wrong？
That is why... I love you？ ...I'm kidding.
I'm sorry, I couldn't hear it, can you say it again！
...Don't lie！ Hehe, geez...
(Okay, I'll do our best next time！)
Manaka
Huh？ What's wrong？
Ah... Well, you're looking great and your body is in good shape.
Maybe my efforts are showing out！
You look so nice when you're in the court.
I would be glad if it was just normal.
I'm sorry. I was just thinking...
(I'm feeling embarrassed.)
(I did my best this time！)
Manaka
Please tell me what you think after breaking records one after another.
There are still more, so I want to aim higher！
What do aim for？
My gold medal is in the future, right？
Please give it to me now！
Hehe！
I will give you a reward for your hard work.
Let's do out best while being careful▼
(Okay, I have to do my best！)
(I did my best trying to do some exercise this time！)
Manaka
▲主人公＊▲.
▲高嶺＊＊▲. Yo！
Yo. Hehe！ You're doing great, right？
Well, I think I'm doing great！
I also secretly stand taller next to you. I'm kidding.
It's not a secret, it's okay to be proud！
Yup... Thank you.
Tell me if you get tired？ I'll give you a massage, okay？
(Okay, I'll do my best！)
(I did my best this time！)
Manaka
What's wrong？ You're spacing out, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Ah, I'm sorry. Um... I think you're getting stronger...
That's why, I was getting a little thrilled...
That much？
...Yeah. When you get closer, you can hear the beating of my heart...
(...Alright, I'll do my best！)
(I did my best this time！)
Manaka
Good work, ▲主人公＊▲.
Good work to you too. Hmm？ You look happy, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Yes, because of your great success.
I know you're doing your best... And that makes me very happy.
I see. Thank you！
Yup. I think we can get good results if we continue like this.
You can do it too, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
Hehe, yes. I'll do my best▼
(Let's do our best！)
(I did my best this time！)
But, I'm a little tired...
Manaka
You won the rally with manager Tezuka, aren't you tired？
You really understand me, ▲高嶺＊＊▲！
Hehe. There, there.
Everyone said it was amazing. I want to use your practice techniques as reference.
But I still can't compete with you.
Do you want to do our best together？ I'll help you too, okay？
(Okay, let's do our best！)
(I did my best this time！)
Manaka
Did you finish cleaning up, ▲主人公＊▲？
Yes, a while ago.
I knew it, I wish I had come a little earlier.
Yay, it's my victory！
Hehe, geez. If it's a cleaning competition, I won't lose next time.
I wonder if I can help you next time. Okay, it's time to go home.
Good work. Do you want to go home together？
(Let's do our best！)
(I did my best this time！)
Manaka
Hey, how were you able to perform that move before, ▲主人公＊▲？
I don't know. My body moved on it's own！ It's a joke.
Hehe. That was not a joke, but something you wanted to do, right？
That's why I'm practicing so much... I want to play like that.
Recently, you have been in many impressive matches, and I...
...And you？
Geez... I don't care.
(Hmm, I have to do my best next time！)
Manaka
Isn't your form getting a lot more beautiful？
Do you think so？
Yeah. Suzuki-sensei also praised you.
Don't forget about your purpose. I'll be watching over you.
I'll help you too. Put yourself in front of me！
Really？ Then, please... How should I do it？
Eh, are you sure？ Being in front of me is a little...
...Perv.
Just kidding！
Hehe, I get it. I look forward to work with you, Coach▼
(First place in mixed classes relay. I wonder if you were watching me ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
Ah, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Manaka
Congrats...
Thank you？ ...What's wrong？
You know, when you got first place...
I was yelling "You did it！ I love you！".
I see.... What！？
Oh, it's okay. It was just a little embarrassing...
But, I'm happy. You looked so cool getting first place▼
(I'm glad I did my best！)
(Hah～... I swam too much.)
Manaka
▲主人公＊▲.
Ah, ▲高嶺＊＊▲. What's wrong？
You know, when you were in the pool... You looked so cool while swimming.
Thank you...？
I'm kind of nervous. I wonder if it's because you are only wearing trunks. You look so strong.
Really？
Yup.... Hehe. But, you look cool even if you don't swim▼
